  },
  {
    "start": 15.18,
    "end": 22.46,
    "text": "**Anna:** You can work at a {hospital|病院}, a {university|大学}, you can work in a coffee shop."
  },
  {
    "start": 23.2,
    "end": 24.88,
    "text": "**Anna:** Wait a minute."
  },
  {
    "start": 24.88,
    "end": 27.28,
