  {
    "start": 76.8,
    "end": 78.08,
    "text": "**Pete:** Sure, Anna."
  },
  {
    "start": 78.08,
    "end": 80,
    "text": "**Pete:** Maybe you can {help|助ける|/help/|I help my friends.} me"
  },
  {
    "start": 80.22,
    "end": 82.46,
