    "text": "**Anna:** No, not {cold|寒い/冷たい|/koʊld/|The weather is cold today.} code."
  },
  {
    "start": 92.52,
    "end": 100.12,
    "text": "**Anna:** You know, for making phone {apps|アプリ|/æps/|I use many apps on my phone.} or websites, you can make {tons|大量/たくさん|/tʌnz/|I have tons of books.} of money writing {code|プログラミング|/koʊd/|I write code for websites.}."
  },
  {
    "start": 100.22,
    "end": 104.46,
    "text": "**Pete:** {Tons|大量/たくさん|/tʌnz/|I have tons of books.} of money, but I can't {code|プログラミング|/koʊd/|I write code for websites.}."
  },
  {
    "start": 104.46,
    "end": 105.98,
    "text": "**Anna:** Next question."
  },
  {
    "start": 105.98,
    "end": 107.66,
