  },
  {
    "start": 107.98,
    "end": 110.7,
    "text": "**Pete:** Do you mean {drive|運転する|/draɪv/|I drive to work every day.} a race car?"
  },
  {
    "start": 110.62,
    "end": 113.42,
    "text": "**Anna:** It's really hard to be a race car {driver|運転手/ドライバー|/ˈdraɪvər/|Race car drivers are brave.}."
  },
  {
    "start": 113.42,
    "end": 114.94,
    "text": "**Pete:** First you need a race car."
  },
  {
    "start": 114.94,
    "end": 119.18,
    "text": "**Anna:** No, I mean {drive|運転する|/draɪv/|I drive to work every day.} a taxi or {drive|運転する|/draɪv/|I drive to work every day.} a bus."
  },
  {
    "start": 119.36,
    "end": 122.64,
    "text": "**Pete:** No, I always {fall|落ちる/眠る|/fɔːl/|Leaves fall in autumn.} asleep when I {drive|運転する|/draɪv/|I drive to work every day.}."
  },
  {
    "start": 122.64,
    "end": 124.72,
    "text": "**Anna:** Oh, that's not good."
  },
  {
    "start": 124.72,
    "end": 126.48,
    "text": "**Anna:** Next question."
  },
  {
    "start": 126.48,
    "end": 128.32,
