  },
  {
    "start": 131.66,
    "end": 133.98,
    "text": "**Pete:** No, I cannot {teach|教える|/tiːtʃ/|Teachers teach students.}."
  },
  {
    "start": 133.98,
    "end": 135.42,
    "text": "**Anna:** Can you {cook|料理する|/kʊk/|I cook dinner every night.}?"
